column1: # This Spreadsheet should be downloaded as CSV file and used as a argument for the python script that writes this config to the custom firmware
# See also the Google Sheets Script that colors and formats this file for online editing and should be configured in Menu > Extensions > App Scripts
# Line starting with a hash (#) are comments and will be ignored by the python script
# Line starting with a a asterisk (*) are tables separators
# Global_Settings > ConfigName => should be less than 16chars
# LP-300 is IOS Loopy Pro emulating RC-300 track buttons
# Not sure how many chars are possible for banks names and info
# Toogle = <N> means momentary: OnValue is sent when button is pressed and OffValue is sent when button is released
# each line represents a set of messages that are sent at once
